---
import DetailLayout from "../../layouts/DetailLayout.astro";
import { getProjectBySlug } from "../../data/projects";

const project = getProjectBySlug("cyb-org");
if (!project) {
  throw new Error("Project data not found for 'cyb-org'");
}

const {
  title,
  synopsis,
  year,
  domains = [],
  links = [],
  tools,
  language,
} = project;
---

<DetailLayout {title} {synopsis} {year} {domains} {links} {tools} {language}>
  
  <div class="detailImage">
    <img
      src="/projects/cyb-org/cyb-org.png"
      alt="cyb-org diagram"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>

  <section class="text text--compact">
    <h6 class="section">I. RESEARCH FRAMEWORK</h6>
    <p class="subject">CONCEPTUAL FOUNDATIONS</p>
    <p class="text">
      The project begins with three foundational keywords: Experience, Network,
      and Information. Through critical synthesis, these themes converge into
      the broader concept of the Cyborg as a figure of entanglement between the
      human and the technological.
    </p>

    <p class="subject">CASE STUDY FOCUS</p>
    <p class="text">
      To ground the theoretical exploration, I analyzed Motoko Kusanagi, the
      cybernetic protagonist of <em>Ghost in the Shell</em>, as a cultural
      artifact situated at the nexus of human experience, data systems, and
      networked embodiment.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="text">
    <h6 class="section">II. INTERFACE SYSTEM</h6>
    <p class="subject">DIAGRAM STRUCTURE</p>
    <p class="text">
      The final deliverable is a multi-interactive diagram built with
      Cytoscape.js. It enables real-time, user-driven exploration of
      relationships among conceptual nodes.
    </p>

    <p class="subject">DESIGN LOGIC</p>
    <p class="text">
      The interface invites users to navigate overlapping ideas through
      modifiable clusters, foregrounding end-user agency in shaping knowledge
      structures.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="text">
    <h6 class="section">III. SEMIOTIC LAYERS</h6>
    <p class="subject">EXPERIENCE</p>
    <p class="text">
      <a
        class="work-link work-link--external"
        href="/projects/cyb-org/Experience Analysis.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Experience Analysis Essay</a
      >
    </p>

    <p class="subject">NETWORK</p>
    <p class="text">
      <a
        class="work-link work-link--external"
        href="/projects/cyb-org/Network Analysis.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Network Analysis Essay</a
      >
    </p>

    <p class="subject">INFORMATION</p>
    <p class="text">
      <a
        class="work-link work-link--external"
        href="/projects/cyb-org/Information Analysis.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Information Analysis Essay</a
      >
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="text">
    <h6 class="section">IV. DOCUMENTATION</h6>
    <div class="gallery gallery--docs">
      <img src="/projects/cyb-org/1.gif" alt="demo 1" loading="lazy" />
      <img src="/projects/cyb-org/2.gif" alt="demo 2" loading="lazy" />
      <img src="/projects/cyb-org/3.gif" alt="demo 3" loading="lazy" />
      <img src="/projects/cyb-org/4.gif" alt="demo 4" loading="lazy" />
      <img src="/projects/cyb-org/5.gif" alt="demo 5" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </section>
</DetailLayout>
